condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 2, Section I, C | Description :The Borrower shall take all action necessary to carry out themeasures identified in the Environmental Management Plan including screening of the physical cultural resources | Frequency:Quarterly
Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 2, Section II, A.1 | Description :The Borrower shall monitor and evaluate the progress of theProject and prepare Project Reports | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 2, Section II, B (b) and (c) | Description :The Borrower shall prepare on or about September 30,2011, a report integrating the results of the monitoring and evaluation activities | Due Date :31-Oct-2013

Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 2, Section II, C.2 | Description :The Borrower shall prepare and furnish to the Bank as part of theProject Report not later than 45 days after the end of each calendar quarter interim unaudited financial reports | Frequency:Quarterly
Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 2, Section II, C.3 | Description :The Borrower shall have its Financial Statements audited |Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 2, Section II,C.1 | Description :The Borrower shall maintain or cause to be maintained a financialmanagement system | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 2, Section V | Description :The Borrower shall not incur any debt unless the revenues andexpenditures show that the estimated net revenues of the Borrower shall be at least 1.1. times the estimated debt servicerequirements | Frequency :Yearly
The Borrower shall, to the satisfaction of the Bank carry out the ZCT Intermodal Yard works in accordance with the Borrower’ssafeguards plan for such works, dated July 2014.
The Borrower shall, to the satisfaction of the Bank launch the Zagreb Container Terminal (ZCT) concession tender by no later thanDecember 31, 2017.

The Borrower shall, to the satisfaction of the Bank sign the contract for technical assistance on Port Community System (PCS) underthe Connecting Europe Facility (CEF) by no later than January 15, 2018, subject to approval of the PCS by CEF by no later thanAugust 31, 2017.
The Guarantor shall ensure, or cause, to the satisfaction of the Bank the commencement of the civil works procurement for theentire D403 Road by no later than July 31, 2018.
The Guarantor shall ensure, or cause, to the satisfaction of the Bank the completion of the bidding documents for the civil worksprocurement for the entire D403 Road by no later than May 31, 2018.
The Guarantor shall ensure, or cause, to the satisfaction of the Bank the completion of the main design and environmental study forthe entire D403 Road by no later than December 31, 2017.

The Guarantor shall ensure, or cause, to the satisfaction of the Bank the confirmation of the committed financing source for theconstruction of the entire D403 Road by no later than September 30, 2017.
The Guarantor shall ensure, or cause, to the satisfaction of the Bank the launching of the civil works procurement for the ZCTIntermodal Yard by no later than July 31, 2017.

The Guarantor through its min in charge of transport shall ensure,or cause,to the satisfaction of the Bank the carrying out of suchD403 Road works and any land acquisition/ resettlement required in a manner compliant with environ and social impact mitigationprocesses and docum (including preparation of a Resettlement Policy Framework by not later than Sep 30, 2017),duly disclosed andconsulted.
